{"tid":2444920,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Rosé 出道曲〈On the Ground〉觀看次數狂飆　單日成績次數在全球奪冠！","createTime":"2021-03-13T08:12:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-13T17:16:37.000Z","uid":16659,"like":23,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"dfd27acead027f9154a4401e01b2450241adb374","tid":2444920,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T08:12:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_bdaa35d119dd13c72163001f91463809/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-03-13/134239-899949.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_bdaa35d119dd13c72163001f91463809%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-03-13%2F134239-899949.png&h=87d5f325&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nBLACKPINK 的 Ros&eacute; 發行首張個人單曲〈R〉後，不只音源成績傲人，MV 也迅速地締造了新紀錄！<br />\n<br />\n昨天（12 日）中午發行了〈R〉的完整音源和主打歌 &ldquo;On the Ground&rdquo; MV，精心拍攝的 MV 甫公開就掀起熱烈迴響，觀看次數在 24 小時內就飆破 3900 萬人次，拿下 YouTube 當日「24 小時內最多人觀看」的冠軍，同時一舉超越韓國個人女歌手 MV 過去寫下的最佳紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CKZvWhCqx1s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DCKZvWhCqx1s&d=RYsttnILlo6fxd9QfZlXIz4xCSFqVWWaKp6LAuIW5iI%3D&h=93a71e0e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CKZvWhCqx1s</a><br />\n<br />\n截至 13 日中午，&ldquo;On the Ground&rdquo; 已陸續拿下美國、加拿大、墨西哥、西班牙、法國、新加坡、泰國⋯⋯等 51 個國家的 iTunes 熱門歌曲榜冠軍；在這同時，Ros&eacute; 也在 Genie、Bugs 等韓國網站的即時榜上奪冠。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_9739c5d5b69d45b884a015fbf5ec6222/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-03-13/134239-899948.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_9739c5d5b69d45b884a015fbf5ec6222%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-03-13%2F134239-899948.png&h=16acf8ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n明天 Ros&eacute; 就會在 SBS《人氣歌謠》上首度公開表演新歌，到時候一定要準時鎖定播出啊！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（照片或影片來源：YG Entertainment）"},{"pid":"4e457c2371d9340ed2acfeeb239a7da8d6898344","tid":2444920,"uid":255310,"l